data.name: LabelDesc.Text
data.value: File Organizer is a simple and efficient tool designed to help you clean up cluttered folders automatically. It scans the selected directory and organizes your files into categories such as Pictures, Documents, and Miscellaneous, moving each file into the appropriate folder. This makes it easier to keep your system tidy without having to sort everything manually. The program features a clean interface, quick setup, and a massive focus on usability.
